trans-unit.target: 提供有关 <see cref="E:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.OriginalDataRestored" /> 事件的数据。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.OriginalDataRestored> event is raised by a <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject> control when it restores data to its original state.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.OriginalDataRestored>事件由引发<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>控制时它将数据还原到其原始状态。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.OriginalDataRestoredEventArgs.ChangeType%2A> argument provides information about the kind of restoration the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject> control performed, and the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.OriginalDataRestoredEventArgs.ChangeReason%2A> provides information about the reason that this restoration was performed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.OriginalDataRestoredEventArgs.ChangeType%2A>自变量提供有关还原类信息<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>控件执行，与<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.OriginalDataRestoredEventArgs.ChangeReason%2A>提供有关已执行此还原的原因的信息。

trans-unit.source: The following code example creates a <xref:System.Data.DataTable> and a <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>, and binds the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject> to the <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例创建<xref:System.Data.DataTable>和<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>，并将绑定<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>到<xref:System.Data.DataTable>。

trans-unit.source: It then creates an <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject.OriginalDataRestored> event handler.
To test the event, right-click a column letter above the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject> on sheet 1 and then click **Delete** in the shortcut menu.
trans-unit.target: 要测试此事件，请右键单击上方的列字母<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject>在工作表 1，然后单击**删除**的快捷菜单中。

trans-unit.source: The event handler replaces the column and column header data and displays a message indicating what kind of data was restored and the reason that the original data was restored.
trans-unit.target: 事件处理程序替换列和列标题数据，并显示一条指示什么类型的数据已还原消息和，还原原始数据的原因。

trans-unit.source: This example is for a document-level customization.
trans-unit.target: 此示例适用于文档级自定义。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the reason that the original data was restored.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示原始数据已还原的原因。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the kind of restoration performed by a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Excel.ListObject" /> control.
